#{140}{}{So what is your sickness?}
{140}{}{你的病是什么？ -- So what is your sickness?}
#{141}{}{You're very inadequate. It's time to eliminate you!}
{141}{}{你太不称职了。是时候消灭你了！ -- You're very inadequate. It's time to eliminate you!}
#{142}{}{Then I'd better shut up and go away.}
{142}{}{那我最好闭嘴走开。 -- Then I'd better shut up and go away.}
